            <show chara="PriestAngryClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_PriestNoName">哼。你们这些联邦的妖怪，没有信仰心的家伙！</speak>
            <show chara="PriestSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_PriestNoName">还“神圣的节日休战戒约”呢——老祖宗传下来的东西，你们怕是早已经忘光了吧？</speak>
            <show chara="PriestSeriousClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="WarriorClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_WarriorNoName">休得无礼！区区蛮夷，不用心学习大祭司的思想，竟然还敢——</speak>
            <show chara="WarriorClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="OfficerClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_OfficerNoName">——不必多言。</speak>
            <show chara="OfficerClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_OfficerNoName">他们既然心意已决，那我们也只好动手。</speak>
            <show chara="OfficerClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_OfficerNoName">就让你们的野蛮风俗被金星诸神永世诅咒吧！</speak>
