            <show chara="OfficerClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_OfficerNoName">……嗯？</speak>
            <show chara="OfficerClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="PriestCalmClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_PriestNoName">……傻丫头。事已至此，你以为可以用三言两语就把这些人打发回去吗？</speak>
